Spanish

[edit]

Pronunciation

[edit]
  • IPA(key): /koˈxeɾ/ [koˈxeɾ]
  • Rhymes: -eɾ
  • Syllabification: co‧jer

Verb

[edit]

cojer

  1. misspelling of coger
